{"tid":678351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六四事件丶六七暴動不納入中史課程 楊潤雄：沒必要將每件史事納入課程大綱","createTime":"2018-05-26T04:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T10:12:12.000Z","uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"69ff7baf467c3a63d040e83e3bfd73b753db783f","tid":678351,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】教育局公布初中中史科及歷史科的修訂課程大綱，其中香港史不設獨立課題。教育局局長楊潤雄表示，香港史會融入不同中史課題，強調沒有忽略香港史。<br />\n<br />\n至於六四事件及六七暴動沒有納入課程大綱，楊潤雄就指，沒有必要將每件歷史事件都納入課程大綱，相信老師有需要也會教授相關課題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=307134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307134&d=2aExcw5PoHOJBrg3cG3sSP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b57122e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307134&h=bf19e8b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=307134</a>"},{"pid":"3db04e2893d3321294cd7a34e76dec80f64cbed8","tid":678351,"uid":2054,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:40:01.000Z","msg":"死共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a4cd5ab99d66c0c4d4bb1fe8de6c2fd619177f","tid":678351,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:43:00.000Z","msg":"64係鄰國既事，的確無需納入香港史"},{"pid":"6f594f0e01122e88f8e2a9460714349bdb16634f","tid":678351,"uid":57554,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"d3a4cd5ab99d66c0c4d4bb1fe8de6c2fd619177f","tid":678351,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:43:00.000Z","msg":"64係鄰國既事，的確無需納入香港史"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"67暴動呢"},{"pid":"6bd5583ae252d6a873c3ff6c267cdf30257db2d7","tid":678351,"uid":25558,"l